---
description: Parse Palo Alto Networks PAN-OS syslog CSV payloads
args:
  named:
    - name: field
      type: field
      description: Field containing the PAN-OS syslog CSV payload.
---

// Header constants are derived from Palo Alto Networks' syslog field
// description pages. The raw payload is a CSV string whose fourth field is the
// log type and whose fifth field is the subtype for several log families.
// Source: https://docs.paloaltonetworks.com/ngfw/administration/monitoring/use-syslog-for-monitoring/syslog-field-descriptions/traffic-log-fields
